      Methods in com.astamuse.asta4d.web.form.flow.base with parameters of type FormProcessData 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      default String BasicFormFlowHandlerTrait.process(FormProcessData processData)
      This method implement the basic mechanism which performs following things: restore the trace data map which contains all the data in each step retrieve instance of target form data which type is specified by BasicFormFlowHandlerTrait.getFormCls() if the current step is before first, set the render target step by BasicFormFlowHandlerTrait.firstStepName() if the back step is not empty, then set the back step name to render target step else call BasicFormFlowHandlerTrait.processForm(FormProcessData, Object) method to process the retrieved form data, currently in the process method, only #validateForm(FormProcessData, Object) is invoked to perform validation.
      default CommonFormResult BasicFormFlowHandlerTrait.processForm(FormProcessData processData, T form)
      The default process will only call the #validateForm(Object) and sub classes can override this method to add extra process logics such as updating form when validation succeeds.
      default CommonFormResult ValidationProcessor.processValidation(FormProcessData processData, Object form)
      Sub classes can override this method to customize how to handle the validation result
